Frontend (HTML)
● Display the live video feed
● Display the current occupancy count, updated in real time

Automated Alerting
● Reuse the Gmail app password and smtplib setup from the earlier module
● Send an automated email when the occupancy count exceeds 4 people
● Include the detected count and timestamp in the alert
● Prevent duplicate alerts from being sent repeatedly for the same ongoing violation

Deliverables
● Complete project codebase (detection script, Flask backend, HTML frontend, email alert
module)
● A working demonstration showing:
○ Live detection and people count on screen
○ An automated email alert triggered when the count exceeds 4

Constraints
● Use any Object detection model for person detection (pretrained is acceptable)
● Must use Flask for the backend and HTML (with CSS/JS) for the frontend
● Must use Gmail app password authentication for alerts, not OAuth or a third-party email
service
● Alert threshold is fixed at more than 4 people
